org.project

Class CSVParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.project.CSVParser

  • public final class CSVParser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class elaborates the content of a CSV file extracting a List of Articles. NOTE: This class is just a wrapper that exposes the functionalities of the actual parser CSVReader from the package com.opencsvcom.opencsv. It supposes that the CSV organization is the following: CSV Structure: * -Identifier * -URL * -Title * -Body * -Date * -Source Set * -Source
